{"tid":1633418,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港爐石戰記選手在賽後訪問戴上full gear高呼光復香港時代革命","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:46:37.000Z","uid":33775,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbf2c3bcb927261e6a8f2676195c47e106b67f5","tid":1633418,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:55:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/InvenGlobal/status/1180954142396710912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FInvenGlobal%2Fstatus%2F1180954142396710912&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4tiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=67c9dac6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FInvenGlobal%2Fstatus%2F1180954142396710912&h=196587fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/InvenGlobal/status/1180954142396710912</a><br />\n<br />\n香港實行《蒙面法》第二日之後，有市民發起「蒙面遊行」抗議惡法。而喺遊戲界，就有香港電競選手喺參與國際賽事時，以蒙面裝扮出席訪問聲援行動！<br />\n<br />\n話說噚晚係經典卡牌對戰遊戲《爐石戰記》嘅「世界大師職業賽」第7週例行賽事，香港選手blitzchung（聰哥）就喺打贏韓國對手DawN之後，以Full Gear姿態現身直播訪問。台灣嘅主持見到聰哥著到咁恆，都唔講太多，直接叫聰哥大大聲講出個八隻大字！聰哥二話不說，用拆咪兼噴射式口水大叫「光復香港，時代革命！」，就直接完結咗訪問。<br />\n<br />\n片段播出後，有中國網民指聰哥作出「港獨言論」要求遊戲公司介入調查處理，相關片段喺Twitter亦遭到移除，不過仍有好多網民上傳Backup片段，而遊戲商暫時亦未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲內勇戰奪勝；遊戲外亦身體力行抵抗強權。相比起《爐石戰記》，相信聰哥同好多香港人一樣，最希望打贏嘅，係一隻叫做《香城Online》嘅Game。"},{"pid":"e67343c114a5cebb1a68d164261cbba84aa08414","tid":1633418,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfdabceaa9150719086d114bfc703d66e001c50","tid":1633418,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018ecc8f96f7b1f849639e1784f41a9ae2716fba","tid":1633418,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{